<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV66">
<l>iṉṟucāta ṉiṉṟucāta laṉṟiyārum vaiyakat</l>
<l>toṉṟiniṉṟu vāḻtaliṉmai kaṇṭunīca reṉkolō</l>
<l>vaṉṟupāra ḷantapāta pōtaiyuṉṉi vāṉiṉmēṟ</l>
<l>ceṉṟuceṉṟu tēvarāyi rukkilāta vaṇṇamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Other than dying today and later, no one in the world</l>
<l>remains alive, [being] united [with life-breath]. Despite seeing that,</l>
<l>how come the lowly people do not think of the flower[-like] feet</l>
<l>that measured the world the other day, go [up the path of light], reach</l>
<l rend="indent">Heaven, and be a god [there]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
